<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.7.6">
<l>uruviṉār piṟavicē rūṉpoti naramputōl kurampai yuḷpuk</l>
<l>karuvinōy ceytuniṉ ṟaivartām vāḻvataṟ kañci ṉāyēl</l>
<l>tiruviṉār vētanāṉ kaintutī vēḷviyō ṭaṅka māṟum</l>
<l>maruviṉār vallavāḻ collumā vallaiyāy maruvu neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you fear your five [senses] thriving, entering into the hovel</l>
<l rend="indent">of a bundle of flesh, skin, and sinew</l>
<l>That combined at your bodily birth, afflicting [you],</l>
<l rend="indent">and persistently creating illness,</l>
<l>Oh, heart, firmly embrace the way that tells of Vallavāḻ,</l>
<l rend="indent">[the city of] those who embrace</l>
<l>The four propitious Vedas, the five fire sacrifices,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the six branches [of knowledge].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
